stop supplies. 

** Supplies be hanged, my dear woman ! " 



 131 

said their delightful friend. " Leave supplies 
to me — I '11 take care of supplies." 

Mrs. Wix hesitated. " Well, it *s exactly 
because I knew you 'd be so glad to do so 
