**So you are doing what you want?" 
Maisie asked. 

** Rather, Miss Farange." 

Miss Farange turned it over. " And she 's 
doing the same ? " 

" Up to the hilt." 

Again she considered. " Then, please, 
what may it be?" 

" I would n't tell you for the whole world." 

She gazed at a gaunt Madonna ; after which 
