I 've said too much to you." 

"Well, you know, I'll never tell," said 
Maisie. 

" No, it's all for yourself. Good-bye." 

" Good-bye." Maisie kept his hand long 
enough to add : " I like you^ too." And 
then supremely: " You do love her? " 



